{"tid":1310503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公文匯傳媒集團員工遇襲　警拘兩人","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T20:13:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1c6b22ae1da444f3dec78b72684a70bd9e8675","tid":1310503,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190713/s00001/0680231aad304c09a6ab054cd63fe0a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190713%2Fs00001%2F0680231aad304c09a6ab054cd63fe0a6.jpg&h=85380303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大公文匯傳媒集團一名56歲姓黃男員工，本月2日4時許偕同事從田灣海傍道的公司外出用膳，當步至田灣街一行人天橋電梯口時，遭兩名黑衣人撲出持木棍毆打；逞兇者其後朝魚市場道方向逃去，黃某手腳受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n警方前晚分別在灣仔區及九龍城區拘捕一名22歲劉姓本地男子及一名20歲陳姓本地男子，涉嫌傷人。被捕男子現正被扣留調查。案件交由西區警區重案組人員跟進調查。"},{"pid":"416b1dd7dd14e47d4390d3229d398bda4e4e2278","tid":1310503,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190713/s00001/1562949631000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190713%2Fs00001%2F1562949631000%2F&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=5373259d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190713%2Fs00001%2F1562949631000%2F&h=4fe02d41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190713/s00001/1562949631000/</a>"},{"pid":"364b8cd89560627522222fd2a3e6a4b8a3b1853b","tid":1310503,"uid":278168,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"藍絲打人唔見警犬捉得咁快，捉完仲要放"},{"pid":"7d8386fca3c252113544613b2b7741c5e1940948","tid":1310503,"uid":50347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"594999e84b79576ddb5a2c314e264550fc874bcf","tid":1310503,"uid":37528,"